commit message: Fix NoSuchElement when using search function in library fragment.

- Fix crash when searching and library is empty.
- Fix crash when resuming app with recents button.

- Fix nullpointer when connecting.
- Another fix to open and close the database properly.
Fix crash on tablets when reopening player.

- Use a semaphore when updating playlist sparsearry.
- Update playlist when a track was added / deleted.
Fix nullpointer when opening donate fragment and no google apps are installed.
Check if multicast lock is held before trying to release it.
Change buildsetup to match new dependency repo.
